      <title>南非谴责货运铁路垄断</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/transnet-south-africa-rebukes-rail-monopoly-over-performance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非政府严厉批评了国有铁路货运垄断企业 Transnet SOC 有限公司 (Transnet SOC Ltd.) 的业绩不佳以及未能提高运量。]]></description>
